12 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 63 O.S. 2021, Section 1-2711, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 1-2711. A. The Legislature recognizes that there is a
15 need to:
16 1. Upgrade the availability of quality dental care services for
17 the people of Oklahoma;
18 2. Improve the balance of dental manpower distribution in the
19 state by geographic location; and
20 3. Increase access to dental care to those who are dependent on
21 the state for necessary dental care;
22 4. Allow providers to work at the top of their license and
23 utilize supporting roles; and
24 5. Address the need for dental faculty.
