1 B. The purpose of the Oklahoma Dental Loan Repayment Act shall
2 be to:
3 1. Increase the number of dentists serving and caring for those
4 dependent upon the state for dental care; and
5 2. Ensure that dental care and services are accessible
6 throughout the state, and specifically, that quality dental care and
7 services be accessible to underserved dental areas in rural and
8 metropolitan areas of the state, and to those dependent upon the
9 state for dental care.
